OL,3,CJust Stop Oil activists convicted over
OL,4,Cprotest at World Snooker Championships
OL,6,FA Just Stop Oil activist who covered a
OL,7,Fsnooker table with orange powder
OL,8,Fduring World Championships in
OL,9,FSheffield has been convicted.
OL,11,FEdred "Eddie" Whittingham, 26, was
OL,12,Ffound guilty of causing criminal
OL,13,Fdamage, while 53-year-old Margaret
OL,14,FReid was convicted of attempting to
OL,15,Fcause criminal damage.
OL,17,FWhittingham, a home energy advisor,
OL,18,Ftold a judge his actions were
OL,19,F"reasonable and proportionate in the
OL,20,Flight of the greater threat we are
OL,21,Ffacing from the climate crisis".
