OL,3,CJust Stop Oil activists convicted over
OL,4,Cprotest at World Snooker Championships
OL,6,FThe pair interrupted a match between
OL,7,FRobert Milkins and Joe Perry at The
OL,8,FCrucible last year, causing nearly
OL,9,F#900 worth of damage.
OL,11,FIn footage of the incident shown to
OL,12,Fthe judge, the defendant who was
OL,13,Fwearing a Just Stop Oil T-shirt could
OL,14,Fbe seen releasing the orange substance
OL,15,F- which he told the court was dyed
OL,16,Fcorn starch powder - and kneeling amid
OL,17,Fthe balls on the table before being
OL,18,Fpulled off by security.
