OL,6,FThe clip shown to the court went on to
OL,7,Fshow Reid trying to do the same thing
OL,8,Fon the other table, on the other side
OL,9,Fof the barrier in the theatre, but she
OL,10,Fis tackled by referee Olivier Marteel
OL,11,Fbefore she can get on the table.
OL,13,FWhittingham denied causing damage to a
OL,14,Fsnooker table, owned by the firm
OL,15,FXingpai, and Reid denied attempting to
OL,16,Fcause criminal damage.
