OL,3,CJust Stop Oil activists convicted over
OL,4,Cprotest at World Snooker Championships
OL,6,FHe said he had planned the protest in
OL,7,Forder to draw attention to Just Stop
OL,8,FOil's campaign to change the
OL,9,FGovernment's policy on oil and gas
OL,10,Fextraction, which he told the court
OL,11,Fwas "breaking the law".
OL,13,FWhittingham said: "I didn't intend to
OL,14,Fcause damage, I intended to cause
OL,15,Fdisruption."
OL,17,FHe said he thought it was "highly
OL,18,Fpossible that (the powder) would be
OL,19,Fwiped off, or hoovered off, without
OL,20,Fcausing significant damage to the
OL,21,Fbaize or the table."
