OL,3,CJust Stop Oil activists convicted over
OL,4,Cprotest at World Snooker Championships
OL,6,FHe agreed that his actions caused
OL,7,Finconvenience to those who attended
OL,8,Ffor "peaceful enjoyment" and to the
OL,9,Forganisers of tournament, who had to
OL,10,Fabandon play for the day on the table
OL,11,Fhe targeted.
OL,13,FBut the defendant told the district
OL,14,Fjudge at Sheffield Magistrates Court:
OL,15,F"I consider it reasonable and
OL,16,Fproportionate in the light of the
OL,17,Fgreater threat we are facing from the
OL,18,Fclimate crisis."
