OL,3,CJust Stop Oil activists convicted over
OL,4,Cprotest at World Snooker Championships
OL,6,FGiving her evidence, Reid cited her
OL,7,Flong experience as a conservator in
OL,8,Fthe museum sector, saying she believed
OL,9,Fany powder could have been easily
OL,10,Fremoved without causing damage.
OL,12,FShe described it as an "unpleasant and
OL,13,Fscary thing to do" but said she had
OL,14,Fbeen driven to an "outrageous and
OL,15,Fdisruptive act such as this"
OL,17,FReid said she had "no other effective
OL,18,Foptions" open to her to halt the "pain
OL,19,Fand death and misery" that climate
OL,20,Fchange will bring.
