OL,6,FWhittingham, of May Street, Exeter,
OL,7,Fand Reid, of Low Fellside, Kendal,
OL,8,FCumbria, were given unconditional bail
OL,9,Fand will be sentenced at Sheffield
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court on July 10.
OL,12,FMax Hinchcliffe, of the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service Yorkshire &
OL,14,FHumberside, said: "Edred (Eddie)
OL,15,FWhittingham and Margaret Reid showed
OL,16,Fan utter lack of thought or care for
OL,17,Fthe players at the tournament or the
OL,18,Ffans watching from across the world.
