OL,6,F"The law upholds the right to protest
OL,7,Fbut this must be balanced against the
OL,8,Frights of others and this case shows
OL,9,Fthat when lawful protest crosses the
OL,10,Fline into criminality we won't
OL,11,Fhesitate to prosecute offenders."
